  <prompt>
    Per CLAUDE.md empirical finding (DELTA #8), `WorkAssignmentWizardDialog.tsx:31` contains a cross-package source-path import:

    ```
    import { SendEmailStep } from '../CreateRecordWizard/steps/SendEmailStep';
    ```

    This bypasses the package's public surface and reaches into a sibling source folder by relative path. Now that task 071 has migrated `CreateRecordWizard/steps/SendEmailStep.tsx` to wrap the canonical `<SendEmailStep />` from `@spaarke/ui-components`, replace the relative import with the canonical package import:

    ```
    import { SendEmailStep } from '@spaarke/ui-components';
    ```

    Verify line 31 is still the correct location (may have drifted from task 071's edits — re-grep). Confirm the canonical export name matches (`SendEmailStep`); adjust the import if the package surface uses a different name. Do not change any other lines.

    NOTE per Owner Clarification: All Wave 5 changes ship as a single PR (task 076). Do not push as standalone.
  </prompt>

